description:
BIG BANK & DJ SCREAM chop it up about The Coronavirus, Social Distancing & Quarantine. They discuss how this effects the streets, rappers, strippers, DJ's, prisoners and even side chicks! They also discuss how to "adjust your hustle" while the world deals with the COVID 19 crisis.
